{"tid":632957,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黑豹票房力壓鐵達尼　成美國票房三位","createTime":"2018-04-18T01:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T02:41:04.000Z","uid":55421,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"81cec1d8c70dc0cec459e0cdc041a5bdb603bac1","tid":632957,"uid":55421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"隨著 Marvel 超級英雄宇宙不斷擴張，於今年 1 月上映的《黑豹》（Black Panther）成功創下票房傳奇，力壓由詹士‧金馬倫執導， 1997 年上映的愛情電影經典《鐵達尼號》（Titanic）。成為美國國內票房歷史以來，票房收入第三名的電影，亦是首部打入美國票房榜前五位的英雄動作電影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據票房記錄網站 Box Office Mojo 的數據顯示，《黑豹》的美國票房收入為約 6.7億美元（約港幣 HK$ 52.3 億元），距離榜首的《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars: The Force Awakens）相差約2.7億美元（約港幣 HK$ 21.3 億元）。讓《黑豹》成為歷史上首部打入本土票房五大電影的英雄電影，同時定亦是一部有關種族多元的作品，讓「多元作品不好賣」的迷思灰飛煙滅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國本土票房收入最高的五部電影（美元）：<br />\n<br />\n星球大戰：原力覺醒（Star Wars: The Force Awakens）：US$936,662,225<br />\n<br />\n阿凡達（Avatar）：US$760,507,625<br />\n<br />\n黑豹（Black Panther）：US$665,630,708<br />\n<br />\n鐵達尼號（Titanic）：US$659,363,944<br />\n<br />\n侏儸紀世界（Jurassic World）：US$652,270,625<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：Box Office Mojo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/16/black-panther-box-office/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2Fblack-panther-box-office%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=ZchohgaxB9QG9V%2BAmERvXYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=a8127c58\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/16/black-panther-box-office/movie-2/</a>"},{"pid":"0f389c33053168d28893268319f507828be1bb5c","tid":632957,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1533d2410ec9e4479fbe99530edda8ed8ae10b4","tid":632957,"uid":120908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"D飛慢慢加價，點都會超越"},{"pid":"6b221f336ab2da8ce6c879f7bfb7a2da2e7fd1bb","tid":632957,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"